WEBVTT

00:00.413 --> 00:02.348
<i>Previously on The Secret Life of</i>
<i>the American Teenager...</i>

00:03.159 --> 00:05.727
You know, I think we have to do something
about these sleeping arrangements.

00:06.010 --> 00:08.645
Our bed in the living room
like I suggested before?

00:08.680 --> 00:09.980
Or get a couch
that pulls out or something.

00:10.014 --> 00:11.748
Does it make you sad
to be in here?

00:11.783 --> 00:13.650
I don't come in this room.

00:13.685 --> 00:15.652
I need you to help me get rid
of everything in this nursery.

00:15.687 --> 00:17.020
What do you wanna do
with all that stuff?

00:17.055 --> 00:18.822
My dad's got you
working for him today?

00:18.856 --> 00:20.624
Honored to be here.

00:20.658 --> 00:21.892
This is my first job back.

00:21.926 --> 00:22.993
After I lost a baby.

00:23.027 --> 00:24.628
I told you what
Adrian called me about,

00:24.662 --> 00:25.829
now you tell me what
Adrian called you about.

00:25.863 --> 00:27.964
She's got some crazy
plan she's come up with

00:27.999 --> 00:29.900
and you're playing
right into it.

00:29.934 --> 00:32.002
I'm gonna have
another baby.

00:32.036 --> 00:34.638
You took everything out of
here without even telling me?

00:34.672 --> 00:35.772
I thought you'd be happy.

00:35.807 --> 00:37.074
She was my
daughter, too!

00:40.812 --> 00:42.679
I want you to come over
to my apartment sometime,

00:42.714 --> 00:44.114
but I want your mom
to know where you are.

00:44.148 --> 00:46.883
I broke up with Madison.
I'm still in love with you.

00:46.918 --> 00:48.719
I'm sorry we're late.
You're drunk?

00:51.089 --> 00:52.823
You go to bed
and I'll do the laundry.

00:52.857 --> 00:54.624
When I'm finished,
I'll get in bed with you.

00:54.659 --> 00:55.859
<i>I've been thinking about you.</i>

00:55.893 --> 00:57.961
<i>And I know you've</i>
<i>been thinking about me.</i>

00:57.995 --> 00:59.129
<i>Haven't you?</i>

